00:15:53,714 --> 00:15:57,260
Yeah, I really thought
I was the one who deserved a spanking.

277
00:15:58,177 --> 00:16:00,721
- So you'll call me?
- Count on it.

278
00:16:01,806 --> 00:16:05,059
