289
00:17:31,604 --> 00:17:33,064
Come in, sit down.

290
00:17:33,230 --> 00:17:35,649
Thanks. Listen...

291
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:39,153
- Boy, this is tough.
- Okay, okay, maybe...

292
00:17:39,320 --> 00:17:41,781
I can make it easier for you.

293
00:17:41,947 --> 00:17:43,491
Judith...

294
00:17:44,075 --> 00:17:46,243
I will always love you...

295
00:17:47,995 --> 00:17:50,039
but there's no going back for me.

296
00:17:50,206 --> 00:17:53,626
I've learned a lot about myself
in the last year, and I'm growing.

297
00:17:53,793 --> 00:17:56,420
