what we had...

299
00:18:02,218 --> 00:18:04,303
but I have to fertilize my shrub.

300
00:18:06,722 --> 00:18:09,558
- What are you talking about?
- It's Berta's metaphor.

301
00:18:09,725 --> 00:18:13,312
The... The bottom line is:
I don't want to reconcile.

302
00:18:13,479 --> 00:18:15,231
